node.text:
Can you relate? 🙋🏻‍♀️ I needed this reminder today and for those of you who are also going through a major shift in your journey know that things get harder before a major breakthrough. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
That means you’re on track and this is just another 🏔mountain you have to climb before you get there. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
It’s ok to cry yourself to sleep as long as the next day you get up with a positive mindset and keep moving forward. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
There is light at the end of the tunnel. Most people give up before they see it. Don’t let that be you. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Keep pushing. Small steps compound into giant ones. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Share this with someone in your life who needs a reminder. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
XO,
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
P💓
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
@womanceomindset

node.text:
How to Improve Your Skill Set & Increase Your Income, Impact, And Influence.👇🏼

Your daily activities will make you or break you.🤯 Here's why! 👇🏼

You can be the most talented. 

You can be the smartest in the room. 

You can be the most outgoing. 

You can even be amazing at what you do....but 

If you are not consistent in doing the daily work that needs to be done to accomplish your goal or target you will fall behind and be in the same place you are now a year from now. 

I get asked this question every day. 

Paula, what is the secret behind your growth? How did you grow a community of over 700k entrepreneurs organically in only two years? 

I know you don't want to hear this but here it goes. 😳

✨✨CONSISTENTLY APPLYING WHAT I LEARN✨✨

I’m not the most talented or the smartest in the room but guess what.... 

I'm determined, committed, hard-working and consistency is my middle name.... 🤓😆

👉🏼Showing up every single day on Instagram.

(I have literally posted every single day for the last 2 years except for one time, not once but anywhere between 2-4 times per day)

👉🏼Consistently creating content that inspires, educates and entertains our community. 

👉🏼Engaging with our community and outside of our community every single day through DM’s, comments, and emails. 

👉🏼 Consistently testing Hashtag groups and strategies until we broke the code and now are able to rank in the top 9 post on almost every hashtag we use by reaching thousands of people who are not yet following us. 

👉🏼Learning and investing in my education every single day. 

👉🏼 Consistency is the bridge from having a target and actually achieving it. 

It's not easy.... But it’s worth it. 

If you are ready to be consistent and put in the work required to grow a massive community on Instagram for your business or personal brand then Dm the word “IGebook”

I will send you the link to join the waitlist for my new ebook 

THE ULTIMATE INSTAGRAM BLUEPRINT 🎉

You can also click the link in bio to get on the VIP waitlist and take advantage of the 50% off and the 2 added bonuses 💃🏻🍾

Remember nothing will change unless you do. 

Paula 💗

node.text:
Want to know how I grew to 100k in 6 months and to 700k in 26 months? 🤑🎉[Swipe 👈🏼]
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
TAG + SHARE this with a woman entrepreneur who is focused on growing her biz. 📈💃🏻
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
➡ Encourage engagement - ask your audience questions and include calls to action on all posts.  Encourage them to save, tag, comment and share your posts just like I did in the beginning of this caption. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
➡ Use all the tools IG offers - don’t restrict yourself just to one format (e.g. images in your feed). Use posts, Stories, Reels, Guides and Live. If you can only focus on a few then go for feed posts, stories and reels. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
➡ Post videos - more and more people are watching - and engaging with - video content whether it’s IG Stories, Reels, Lives or IGTV.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
➡ Engage more, not just on your own account - every time you engage with a non-follower on another post is an opportunity for them to follow you. Be strategic though, find large accounts in your niche that serve your ideal audience and engage with their followers. (Engage not spam)
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
➡ Be consistent, both in brand but also in posting. If you’re posting something where your audience will go “Huh?” then it probably isn’t right for that account. Stick to your niche and area of expertise.  Position yourself as the expert in that specific industry.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Click the  link on our bio to join the waitlist for THE ULTIMATE INSTAGRAM BLUEPRINT my new ebook  Or Dm me the word “ IGebook” to get the link. 🙋🏽‍♀️
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
You don't have to figure this out on your own.  In my ebook you will find every strategy I used to grow to over 700k followers in two years and how my Instagram turned into a 
6-figure business. 🚀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
It's your turn.  Are you in? Link in bio. 🔗
